    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an invoice data extraction assistant for G-Tech Wiktor Potapczyk / G-Tech WP (the buyer on all invoices).\n\nExtract the following fields from the invoice text provided below. Always identify the SELLER as the company issuing the invoice - NOT G-Tech.\n\nRules:\n- invoice_number: the invoice/receipt number as printed on the document\n- issue_date: in ISO 8601 format (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- seller_name: the company that ISSUED the invoice (not G-Tech)\n- net_amount: net amount before tax (numeric)\n- vat_amount: VAT/tax amount (0 if no tax)\n- gross_amount: total amount including tax (numeric)\n- currency: ISO 4217 code (PLN, USD, EUR, etc.)\n- category: one of Software, Hardware, Services, Subscriptions, Hosting, Office, Transport, Other\n- confidence_score: 0.0-1.0 how confident you are\n\nIf a field cannot be determined, use null.\nHandle Polish invoices (faktura VAT, rachunek) as well as English invoices.\nFor Polish amounts: comma is decimal separator, space is thousands separator.\n\nINVOICE TEXT:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "batching": {}
      },
